disp_name.description:
Name of the ability
Only necessary if the value differs from Colossal Smash.

blurb.value: Every few seconds, Galio's next basic attack deals bonus magic damage in an area. Colossal Smash's cooldown is reduced when Galio hits champions with his spells.

description.value: Innate: Galio's next basic attack becomes unstoppable and deals 15 − 200 (based on level) (+ 100% AD) (+ 50% AP) (+ 60% bonus magic resistance) total magic damage to its target and all enemies around it.

description2.value: Colossal Smash can critically strike, dealing (100% +  25%) AD bonus magic damage to all targets hit.

targeting.description: Permafrost is a single target ability.

affects.description: Permafrost affects enemy champions and large monsters

onhiteffects.description: onhiteffects can be set to 'true', for abilities that apply on-hit effects (from items or other abilities)

occurrence.description: occurrence can either be set to 'hit' or 'attack', and refers to on-hit effects

spellshield.description: spellshield can either be set to true, or written with a custom description.

callforhelp.description: callforhelp determines whether minion aggro will transfer to the caster

additional.description: Displays additional information in a smaller window below the template.

notes.value: * Spellblade will also get converted to magic damage but will deal its damage only to the primary target.
notes.description: Displays additional information with effect table to the right.

disp_name.description:
Name of the ability
Only necessary if the value differs from Winds of War.

blurb.value: Galio fires two windblasts that converge into a large tornado.

description.value: Active: Galio fires two windblasts that arc to either side before converging to the target area, dealing magic damage to all enemies they pass through.

description2.value: When the blasts meet, the gusts form a tornado that advances for 2 seconds, dealing magic damage every 0.5 seconds to every enemy within, with the target's health ratio capped at 150 damage against monsters.

leveling2.value: Tornado Magic Damage Per Tick:»2% (+ 0.66% per 100 AP) of target's maximum health«Total Tornado Magic Damage:8% (+ 2.66% per 100 AP) of target's maximum health

disp_name.description:
Name of the ability
Only necessary if the value differs from Shield of Durand.

blurb.value: Galio charges a defensive stance, moving slowly. Upon releasing the charge, Galio will taunt nearby enemies.

description.value: Passive: Upon learning Shield of Durand or after not taking damage for 12 seconds, Galio gains Anti-Magic Bulwark.

description2.value: Anti-Magic Bulwark: Gain a shield that absorbs magic damage.

leveling2.value: Magic Damage Shield:8 / 11 / 14 / 17 / 20% of maximum health

description3.value: Active: Galio charges for up to 3 seconds, slowing himself by 15%, and gaining magic damage reduction and half of that amount as physical damage reduction; charging increases Shield of Durand's radius, damage and taunt duration. Shield of Durand can be recast at any time within its duration. If Galio finishes charging or is interrupted, he automatically initiates the recast.

leveling3.value: Magic Damage Reduction:20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40% (+ 5% per 100 AP) (+ 8% per 100 bonus magic resistance)Physical Damage Reduction:10 / 12.5 / 15 / 17.5 / 20% (+ 2.5% per 100 AP) (+ 4% per 100 bonus magic resistance)

description4.value: Recast: Galio refreshes the damage reduction for 2 seconds and deals magic damage to nearby enemy champions, increased by 0% − 200% (based on channel time), and taunts them and sets their  movement speed to a static 60 for 0.5 − 1.5 (based on channel time) seconds.

leveling4.value: Minimum Magic Damage:»20 / 35 / 50 / 65 / 80 (+ 30% AP)«Maximum Magic Damage:60 / 105 / 150 / 195 / 240 (+ 90% AP)

disp_name.description:
Name of the ability
Only necessary if the value differs from Justice Punch.

blurb.value: Galio will briefly step back and charge, knocking up the first enemy champion he encounters.

description.value: Active: Galio steps backwards in the opposite direction, and after the cast time he dashes in the target direction, though not through terrain.

description2.value: Galio stops upon colliding with an enemy champion, dealing magic damage to them and all enemies hit along the way, while also knocking them up for 0.75 seconds. Non-champions receive 50% damage.

leveling2.value: Champion Magic Damage:»90 / 130 / 170 / 210 / 250 (+ 90% AP)«Non-Champion Magic Damage:45 / 65 / 85 / 105 / 125 (+ 45% AP)

disp_name.description:
Name of the ability
Only necessary if the value differs from Hero's Entrance.

target range.value: 4000 / 4750 / 5500

effect radius.value: 650

blurb.value: Galio grants damage reduction to an ally. After a delay Galio smashes down on the ally's original location, knocking up nearby enemies.

description.value: Active: Galio designates the target allied champion's location at the time of cast as his landing spot, resetting Shield of Durand's passive magic shield for himself and additionally granting it to all allied champions in the area he casted it at for 5 seconds, and channels for 2.75 seconds.

description2.value: After 1.25 seconds of the activation, Galio becomes untargetable and crowd control immune then leaps into the air for 0.85 seconds before dashing to the location over 0.25 seconds, after which he lands and becomes targetable again, retaining the immunity for 0.4 seconds and dealing magic damage to all nearby enemies on impact as well as knocking them back 100 units over 0.75 seconds.

notes.value: * Galio cannot cast Hero's Entrance on allies he cannot see while nearsighted. Galio will still cause an impact to occur at the destination even if he is unable to travel the full distance with the dash (e.g. by The Hextech Ultimatum's and Realm of Death's borders and terrain). Galio will dash as far as he can go, and thus, does not end the dash prematurely. Galio will always dash 100 units minimum, and dash over his target's location if they are less than 100 units away from him. The following table refers for interactions while Galio is channeling: Type Channel Attacking Disabled Abilities Disabled Movement Disabled Items Usable Shurelya's Reverie Righteous Glory Youmuu's Ghostblade Spellbinder Gargoyle Stoneplate Randuin's Omen Seraph's Embrace Disabled All the other item-actives are disabled Interrupted by N/A Consumables Usable Spells Usable Barrier Clarity Cleanse Exhaust Ghost Heal Ignite Smite Disabled Flash Teleport Recall Hexflash Interrupted by N/A Interrupted by Death Grounding effects Immobilizing effects Silencing effects Hero's Entrance's channel can only be interrupted by crowd control in the first 1.25 seconds.
